Name: Birth Patrol
About the game: 2D shoot 'em up in which you play as Jill the birth control pill and go back in time and abort Hitler. Gameplay: Laser attacks! Time-Nazis! Rail shooter section! Fetus Hitler boss battle! WASD controls! Arrow keys work, TOO! This is my first project as a solo developer! If you have any suggestions and feedback, please leave a comment. If there is enough interest, I will release more levels.
